data.description: Nestled in a sought after area by Club Lake and Million dollar Estates on a dead end road.  This Charming Country Property offers Tranquility with Beautiful Views.Custom Brick home on 5.67 acres.Family Room w-Fireplace,Spacious Kitchen w-Breakfast Bar,Lots of Cabinet and Counter Space,eat in Kitchen, Barn Doors on your Formal Dining area w-tons of Windows or could be work from home Office. Primary Suite has a sitting area with ensuite  that boasts a separate Shower, jetted tub to soak in after long a day,dual sinks and 2 WIC,Laundry Room will not disappoint.2 Bedrooms on the other side of the house are oversized with built in desk and large closets. Gameroom for all those family game nights.Chicken Coop and Dog pen already in place along with a Garden and storage building..Bring the 4 Wheelers,Kids and animals this acreage is ready for your family. 32 Solar Panels with Battery Backup, 2023 Dishwasher, 11-22 HVAC system , 2021 Windows,Roof,Gutters,Flooring,Interior,Exterior Paint.
